```jac
with entry {
    result = sandbox.exec_command("jac-sbx-abc123", "ls -la /app", timeout=30);
    print(result["stdout"]);
}
```

#### Log Retrieval

```jac
with entry {
    result = sandbox.logs("jac-sbx-abc123", offset=0);
    print(result["content"]);
    # result["offset"] contains the byte offset for the next read (streaming)
}
